<h2><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"What_is_a_Hogshead.3F">What is a Hogs=
head?</span></h2>
<p>A hogshead is a traditional unit of volume. It was mostly used for measu=
ring liquids like wine, beer, or cider. It was also used for other goods, s=
uch as sugar or tobacco. Imagine a very large wooden barrel; that's often w=
hat a hogshead refers to.</p><div class=3D"toc" style=3D"background:none; b=
order:none; padding:0;"><div class=3D"thumbinner" style=3D"width:302px;">

<ins class=3D"adsbygoogle" style=3D"display:inline-block;width:300px;height=
:250px" data-ad-client=3D"ca-pub-2806779683782082" data-ad-slot=3D"43199649=
85" data-adsbygoogle-status=3D"done">
